{"tid":1074643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幼稚園校長余倩瑛失蹤已兩天 家人憂心急尋","createTime":"2019-03-23T13:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T16:34:00.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"19071307643584c9dbfbf6b158e2b9ef944b0939","tid":1074643,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190323/large/1553348654_e7da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190323%2Flarge%2F1553348654_e7da.jpg&h=896702f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n45歲幼稚園女校長余倩瑛本月21日（前日）上午離開其位於藍田連德道住所後不知失終，其家人憂心不已，同日向警方報案，並透過網上發帖，望市民幫忙提供線索，警方今午亦公開呼籲市民提供這名失蹤女子的消息。<br />\n<br />\n失蹤者余倩瑛，是葵涌葵盛東邨保良局李俊駒伉儷幼稚園的校長。警方指她身高約1.63米，體重約50公斤，尖臉、瘦身材及蓄長直黑髮。她最後露面時身穿淺藍色外套、黑長褲黑鞋、戴眼鏡及帶著紫色手袋。警方呼籲若任何人如有該失蹤女子的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 0321或9886 0060與東九龍總區失蹤人口調查組聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n據失蹤者的親友指，余女平日做事有熱誠兼極有交帶，難以明白她何以無故失蹤。她平日多在藍田及葵盛東區出沒，每日放學後都多會第一時間返家陪伴母親，從未試過失聯，但前日起她不知所終，手機亦聯絡不上，令家人憂心不已。據悉，余倩瑛21日失蹤當天，有人曾目擊到與她樣貌相似的女子曾乘搭88X巴士，巴士當時正往沙田方向行駛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190323/59404240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59404240&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=8042ad41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59404240&h=d930bceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190323/59404240</a>"},{"pid":"ff8ed0246542209d3254b4038b1b28b39582f3c7","tid":1074643,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:00:26.000Z","msg":"佢好安全"},{"pid":"9f901589d8fc7db024e8a9b4d11607792671cc05","tid":1074643,"uid":2419,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"點解唔係羅校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd791a884ae6349095586d0c44637df33924891","tid":1074643,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff8ed0246542209d3254b4038b1b28b39582f3c7","tid":1074643,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:00:26.000Z","msg":"佢好安全"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"are you sure. 廢老岩食"},{"pid":"9112860c95c9b415259d536fd32cebcccd3b59d8","tid":1074643,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:06:01.000Z","msg":"似單身"},{"pid":"a0596cea21343c1166905503867d03f8afac4179","tid":1074643,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c8c0731a7ae70ea86bfdf9d3eb395713ad0edf9f","tid":1074643,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:34:00.000Z","msg":"女人有無可能14日行政拘留"}]}